    <section>
        <title>Single Server Configuration</title>
        <para>An example setup of a single Tomcat server running MySQL server:<itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>CentOS v5.3 x64</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>4 GB Ram</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Intel Q6600 Quad Core Processor or better</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>1 TB RAID 1 configuration – SATA II 3.0 Gbps</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Apache</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Tomcat</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>MySQL 5.1.x</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist></para>
    </section>
